@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> Archived : cancel
Archived --> Reviewed : confirm
Archived : entry / log reservation
Reviewed --> Completed : approve
Completed --> Archived : revert
Completed --> [*]
@enduml